{"tid":17701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[CCTVB唔會講] 印度會係2017年1月一次過射83粒衛星","createTime":"2016-12-02T02:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T05:39:56.000Z","uid":25424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a0bc71915440c08e603e8c4ac73a5b9d83fdfab","tid":17701,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.thehindu.com/sci-tech/science/ISRO-to-launch-83-satellites-in-one-go-in-Jan./article16730366.ece\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsci-tech%2Fscience%2FISRO-to-launch-83-satellites-in-one-go-in-Jan.%2Farticle16730366.ece&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c5c88875\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thehindu.com/sci-tech/science/ISRO-to-launch-83-satellites-in-one-go-in-Jan./article16730366.ece</a><br />\n<br />\n印度會係出年一月，一次過送83個衛星上太空，其中80顆係幫歐洲，美國，以色列等等國家既衛星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 挑戰新紀錄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB只會自欺欺人呃廢老，成日幫支那火箭打飛機<br />\n但係佢永遠唔會報印度已經攬左好多商業衛星發射既生意，接到既生意數量係亞洲數一數二<br />\n而且印度既印度太空研究組織（ISRO），而經玩緊火星任務，好多國家開始都想搵印度幫手射上去火星<br />\n而支那仲只係玩緊月球，仲用緊隻月亮死兔去打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為印度發射成本極平，成功率又高，尤其係低軌道，直情最撚平係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84b5fbf73d84c026dc2674d299936427eef26ab","tid":17701,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efb9b0339ef001454f96f500087c6ddd356eb81","tid":17701,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:47:35.000Z","msg":"講多d"},{"pid":"f829449747f858821dc895117775017bc334ed14","tid":17701,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:18:33.000Z","msg":"一箭雙星定真係一日射3 支<br />\n有無多d 資料睇下"},{"pid":"159058ae68b1c9611a65fa18641ae909cc2a2f42","tid":17701,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講多d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印度地理得天獨厚，國家位置近赤道，射上去既火箭可以用少D燃料，燃料重量細左就可以載多D衛星<br />\n印度依家通常用既火箭發射場係Sriharikota呢個島<br />\n<a href=\"https://maps.google.com.hk/maps?rlz=1C9BKJA_enHK649HK649&amp;hl=en-GB&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;fb=1&amp;gl=hk&amp;entry=s&amp;sa=X&amp;ll=13.7423784,80.2098219&amp;z=12&amp;ftid=0x3a4d9895e44ee6c5:0x9556114b59dc6011&amp;q=Sriharikota,+Andhra+Pradesh+524124,+India&amp;gmm=CgIgAQ%3D%3D&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiP1uLIw9TQAhVCl5QKHXtKDbsQ8gEIJTAB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaps.google.com.hk%2Fmaps%3Frlz%3D1C9BKJA_enHK649HK649%26hl%3Den-GB%26um%3D1%26ie%3DUTF-8%26fb%3D1%26gl%3Dhk%26entry%3Ds%26sa%3DX%26ll%3D13.7423784%2C80.2098219%26z%3D12%26ftid%3D0x3a4d9895e44ee6c5%3A0x9556114b59dc6011%26q%3DSriharikota%2C%2BAndhra%2BPradesh%2B524124%2C%2BIndia%26gmm%3DCgIgAQ%253D%253D%26ved%3D0ahUKEwiP1uLIw9TQAhVCl5QKHXtKDbsQ8gEIJTAB&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7c8d706e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://maps.google.com.hk/maps?rlz=1C9BKJA_enHK649HK649&amp;hl=en-GB&amp;um=1&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;fb=1&amp;gl=hk&amp;entry=s&amp;sa=X&amp;ll=13.7423784,80.2098219&amp;z=12&amp;ftid=0x3a4d9895e44ee6c5:0x9556114b59dc6011&amp;q=Sriharikota,+Andhra+Pradesh+524124,+India&amp;gmm=CgIgAQ%3D%3D&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiP1uLIw9TQAhVCl5QKHXtKDbsQ8gEIJTAB</a><br />\n已經有一百二十個衛星由呢個發射場射上去，而印度上次發射既火星軌道探測器，更係第一次玩火星就任務成功，而用既錢仲少撚過荷里活拍既火星任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家印度既新客戶就係Alphabet，即係Google<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c97dd37deae89e3ec698d500418d54a10c2c003","tid":17701,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:26:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一箭雙星定真係一日射3 支<br />\n有無多d 資料睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://indianexpress.com/article/technology/science/isro-aiming-for-world-record-planning-to-put-83-satellites-on-single-rocket-3728209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Ftechnology%2Fscience%2Fisro-aiming-for-world-record-planning-to-put-83-satellites-on-single-rocket-3728209%2F&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8b1e8b79\" target=\"_blank\">http://indianexpress.com/article/technology/science/isro-aiming-for-world-record-planning-to-put-83-satellites-on-single-rocket-3728209/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果無睇理解錯，佢係一支火箭送83粒上去"},{"pid":"a20752e95acdb6e1c69eaab671017ca06f126c6f","tid":17701,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講多d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ece8cd73f4ab53eb2d21d9020f3e889b05c87d7","tid":17701,"uid":1778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"真係唔講唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749648f22e5c2afcacd731d6b49f4eff7feb20fb","tid":17701,"uid":24751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一箭雙星定真係一日射3 支<br />\n有無多d 資料睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://indianexpress.com/article/technology/science/isro-aiming-for-world-record-planni